[:en] # About Piggy Riches<br>
If pigs could be upper class they would probably look like they do in Piggy Riches. Just like the name suggests, the theme of the slot is rich pigs. Fat wallets, full money bags and piggy banks filled to the rim. High hats, furry clothes and diamonds – it’s quickly obvious that these pigs are not under any economic hardships. With generous wilds and a great bonus game with up to 28 Free Spins one truly has the chance to swipe some of the piggy’s riches. The pleasant background sound with the babble from a live casino lobby together with the refreshing sound of someone pouring an ice-filled drink really creates a very nice atmosphere.</li>
