<h2 id="game-features">Game Features</h2>
<p>The slot machine consists of five wheels and three rows and includes both wilds and a generous bonus round with nice features. With a win multiplier of up to 18 times the outcome can quickly become very pleasant.</p>
<h3 id="wild-2">Wild</h3>
<p>The wild symbol in this video slot replaces all symbols except the Free Spins symbol. The rare element of the Piggy Riches wild is that as soon as it is part of a winning bet line, the win is tripled.</p>
<h3 id="scatters-1">Scatters</h3>
<p>Piggy Riches has a unique bonus game where you can get a multiplier of up to 18 times the win. If you hit two Scatter symbols in the main game you’ll win twice the bet amount and if you hit three or more Scatters you’ll enter the bonus round where you get the choice of for example receiving 22 Free Spins with a win multiplier of 2 or 9 Free Spins with a win multiplier of 5. If you hit more Scatters whilst in the bonus round you’ll receive additional Free Spins with a total number of max 28 Free Spins.</p>
